Hey Gang. Effective today, Sunday, 11/17/24, Cookie Plug Uptown will be temporarily closed as we work to optimize our operations. We hope to reopen at a future date. Stay tuned for updates.

We remain committed to providing you with the same great products and service at our Downtown location, just 1/2 block from The Alamo at 507 E Houston St. Pull up today or order online. We can’t wait to see you there!

#CookiePlugSATX #uptown #weareclosed
